cess to cadet email via VMIConnect  Our administrators are working with Microsoft to resolve this problem as quickly as possible  Cadets may still access VMI Email by going directly to www outlook com  Cadets will need to know their MS Live password  which is most likely the initial password used when the account was originally setup  In the event you do not know your password  you can use the option  Can t access your account  to reset your password  If you are unsuccessful doing this  please take your photo ID to the Barracks Help Desk to request your outlook com password be reset  VMI Foundation Keydet Club Alumni Webcams Directories My VMI  RESOURCES   Title IX  Health   Safety   IT   Site Index Parents   Families   Cadets   Non discrimination Statement   Privacy   THE VMI PHILOSOPHY The VMI experience is framed by relevant education within a military environment  It s an education that develops character  fosters a lifelong appreciation of physical fitness engenders a sense of responsibility to others  and cultivates the ability to master adversity  VIRGINIA MILITARY INSTITUTE Lexington  Virginia 24450 General Information   540  464 7230  Admissions  admissions vmi edu 